snippet.title: Aurora Tech
snippet.description:
Welcome to Aurora Tech Channel! 

I'm Aurora Lung from Danville, California.

My brother, Helios, and I make videos on 3D printers, CNC machines, as well as Fusion 360 CAD and CAM. We started this channel back in February 2021. My brother generally prefers to stay behind the scenes but he does randomly pop up sometimes. He's our cameraman and video editor. We plan the videos together, but I do the scriptwriting and mainly host the channel.

Thanks for stopping by, and we hope you enjoy!
